data.description: Priced under any comparable, so if you need cash to close - this is the place! Beautiful, big 3 bed (plus there's an office), 2 bath home in a gated, safe Viera Home! No neighbors in the back...We are West of I-95, next to all the best schools and room for a pool! Newer Roof (2019) Air Handler (2021), Vinyl Fencing, Updated Kitchen...and this home has two (2) distinct living spaces for entertaining, either formal or informal OR separating teens from parents (great for both!). Big garage, large master bath with walk-in closet, and next to the best schools, walking/biking trails and golf cart expeditions in Florida! AND SITTING ROOM!
